posting_body: ['Please feel free to Call or TEXT us for any info or to schedule a tour!', 'Prices and Availability subject to change.', 'Welcome to Capstone at Vallagio', 'Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 98', 'OR Text 98 to', 'show contact info', 'for more information.', 'This is a 2 Bedroom, 2 Bath, approximately 1130 Sq.', 'Ft.', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'South Range Crossings participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,260 | 2 Occupants: $56,280 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,300 | 4', 'Occupants: $70,320 | 5 Occupants: $75,960 | 6', 'Occupants: $81,600.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Inspired by you and designed for your satisfaction, our apartments were crafted for your comfort.', 'Each of our one and two bedroom floor plans is appointed with faux wood flooring, oversized windows, walk-in closets, roller shades, and sleek kitchens complete with quartz countertops, designer cabinets, and stainless steel appliances.', 'Enjoy mountain views from select West-facing balconies.', 'With an incomparable combination of refined style and quality, Lofts at Lincoln Station will surpass your expectations.']
